data.description: Get your little piece of paradise! This 2 bedroom 2 bath manufactured home is on over 3 acres. There is insulated and heated 2 car attached garage, storage shed, partially fenced, den, great room, deck, comp roof, newer carpet, propane heat, on demand water heater, dual pane windows and gutters. Beautiful view off the deck!
